<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='956000' id='t-956000'>I think the process I described,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='958000' id='t-958000'>you know, productivity, quality, patient-centered care,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='962000' id='t-962000'>can give an answer,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='965000' id='t-965000'>and there are many which fit this paradigm.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='967000' id='t-967000'>You take dentistry, hearing aid, maternity and so on.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='970000' id='t-970000'>There are many where this paradigm can now play,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='973000' id='t-973000'>but I think probably one of the most challenging things</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='975000' id='t-975000'>is on the softer side.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
