16:28
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='977000' id='t-977000'>Now, how do you create compassion?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='979000' id='t-979000'>Now, how do you make people own the problem,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='981000' id='t-981000'>want to do something about it?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='983000' id='t-983000'>There are a bit harder issues.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='985000' id='t-985000'>And I'm sure people in this crowd can probably find the solutions to these.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:40
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='989000' id='t-989000'>So I want to end my talk leaving this thought and challenge to you.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
